						               													<description>The Godfather has asked you to collect the revenue from the city's underground bars. This is your chance to put your pockets full of money in the process! But be careful, collaborate with each other to satisfy the sponsor or the story will end very badly...&amp;#10;A game of bluff and influence. You will have to play smart, bluff and reason with the greedy companions who fill their pockets with them at the risk of losing everyone.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Gangster Family, the starting player picks up an envelope of his choice from the Godfather's desk. He reads out loud the amount inside, then draws two money cards (then hiding the amount). He must place one of the 7 cards in his hand in front of him and discard one. He then hands the envelope with the money to his neighbour on his left. It is important that this amount must be strictly higher than the amount given at the beginning. The player on the left then has 2 choices: to believe the amount given away or not. The game ends when all the cards are gone, or when all the envelopes are gone. During the game, you must work together to collect the amount of money offered by the Godfather. If you do, the player with the most money wins the game. If not... then the wrath of the Godfather will catch up with everyone and you will all lose.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
